The paper discusses deep neural networks, specifically convolutional neural networks, and their interpretability and behavior. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on understanding the hidden layers of the neural network, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories.
